  "2026-07-18T09:25:39.141Z",codex-sdk-vcs-20260718,"Hosted review round 1 evidence: legacy extension activation payloads now safely treat absent relationship_kinds registrations as empty in activation summaries and capability usage; compatibility comments document this boundary in summary, usage, graph assembly, and loader surfaces. The public registry remains intentionally strict for required ordering, hierarchy, and allowSelf semantics, with new missing-field acceptance tests. Full sandbox coverage passed: 308 files, 5,896 tests, exact 100/100/100/100."
