  "2026-07-18T15:19:21.805Z",codex-root,"Active tranche evidence: relationship-event mutations can now participate in the public crash-recoverable workspace transaction coordinator without rewriting immutable history. The VCS exemplar proves add/remove/add compensation and replay, conflicting-event reconciliation, concurrent removal safety, and committed-result validation. Exact full coverage and packed VCS acceptance passed. Broader relationship-platform scope remains on this feature after this tranche."
  "2026-07-18T16:49:49.198Z",codex-root,"PR #605 transaction tranche review evidence: relationship-event compensation now removes only the exact transaction-owned commits_to winner, preserves newer unrelated ledger state, journals recovered event identity, and validates both item and relationship state after commit. Exact full coverage and packed VCS acceptance pass. The broader registry/index/graph feature remains open for later slices."
